---
title: Fiesta Salmon Tacos with Pineappe Salsa and Elotes-Inspired Corn
description: Sweet and smoky flavours reign supreme in this salmon taco. Salmon is flavoured by a fragrant Mexican spice blend, then flaked into tortillas with crisp iceberg lettuce, sweet chipotle sauce and fresh pineapple-cucumber slaw. Paired with charred corn "elotes," it's a meal as pretty to look at as it is delicious to eat!
